{"tid":1887102,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】李嘉誠親赴紐西蘭專機空運返港 Safety+ CoverCool 保護衣贈醫護","createTime":"2020-02-19T10:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T15:40:23.000Z","uid":311701,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a665d8a9f29041e031599ec9d27c5a2a3f6bccc5","tid":1887102,"uid":311701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T10:11:39.000Z","msg":"香港目前正處於醫護物資短缺的情況，不少人前線醫護人員亦擔心會因而增加被傳染的風險，不過今日又有好消息。李嘉誠基金會在今日就宣布首批贈送予香港醫護的 N95 口罩已經到達本港，隨機運送的更有從當地醫療機構購買的 5115 件保護衣，將會送給前線醫護人員。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5jpYdbe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5jpYdbe.jpg&h=5b4ce3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李嘉誠基金會在今日中午時分於 Facebook 專頁上分享了一個貼文，分享首批送予香港醫護的 N95 口罩已經到港的喜訊，表示將會送給醫管局以派發予前線的醫護人員。從他們分享的照片中可見，這批口罩多達 84 箱。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c80TMwz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc80TMwz.jpg&h=e620179e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n此外，網上亦流傳了一張李嘉誠在私人飛機上檢查貨品的相片。從相片中可見，箱中裝著的是由紐西蘭醫療機助購的 5,115 件 Safety+ CoverCool Type 5/6 保護衣。從網上資料得知，每箱將裝有 50 件保護衣，可以提供靜電防護以及液體保護，並以背部用上透氣的藍色物料為一大特點。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q2xVZRK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq2xVZRK.png&h=0c4ef736&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xhV4TbT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxhV4TbT.png&h=fd16add8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.msn.com/zh-hk/news/localnews/【武漢肺炎】李嘉誠親赴紐西蘭專機空運返港-safetyplus-covercool-保護衣贈醫護/ar-BB1098ni?ocid=spartanntp&amp;fullscreen=true#image=4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.msn.com%2Fzh-hk%2Fnews%2Flocalnews%2F%E3%80%90%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E%E3%80%91%E6%9D%8E%E5%98%89%E8%AA%A0%E8%A6%AA%E8%B5%B4%E7%B4%90%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E5%B0%88%E6%A9%9F%E7%A9%BA%E9%81%8B%E8%BF%94%E6%B8%AF-safetyplus-covercool-%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E8%A1%A3%E8%B4%88%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%2Far-BB1098ni%3Focid%3Dspartanntp%26fulls